  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/d2fc3ae9b7173393ed904be33b71b85f.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ <strong>TinyCraft Town</strong> is a simple 2D pixel art survival game focused on light resource management, crafting, and exploration. Gather materials, cook food, fish, build workstations, craft weapons and gear, and restore a small ruined village. Inspired by games like RuneScape, Valheim, and Conan Exiles—without the complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>relaxing crafting sim</strong> with satisfying progression, cozy visuals, and no pressure — just you, your tools, and a world to rebuild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.poster.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.webm?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.mp4?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.poster.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.webm?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.mp4?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/c454ff4d6c670fad4388c5396d968bd2.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🪓 What will you do?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ <strong>Gather & Craft</strong> – Chop wood, mine ores, and create workstations and tools to fuel your progress.<br>🏘️ <strong>Rebuild the Town</strong> – Fix abandoned buildings to unlock new features, recipes, and characters.<br>🌱 <strong>Explore & Expand</strong> – Discover new lands and resources as you repair bridges, docks, and passageways.<br>📦 <strong>Strategic Resource Flow</strong> – Optimize your village's productivity and balance your economy.<br>🎵 <strong>Chill Atmosphere</strong> – A cozy pixel world with a soothing soundtrack, perfect for relaxed play sessions.<br>♻️ <strong>Early Access Evolving World</strong> – Frequent content updates and new systems on the horizon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy games like <strong>Forager</strong>, <strong>Travellers Rest</strong>, or <strong>Stardew Valley</strong>, but want something more <strong>focused on crafting and calm progression</strong>, TinyCraft Town is the perfect escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧰 Whether you're here to optimize or just to unwind — your village awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for your visit! I'm a solo indie game developer and I am doing my best to improve the game based on the community feedback. By purchasing the game you are encoraging me to keep making games even better. Best wishes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/d2fc3ae9b7173393ed904be33b71b85f.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🏝️ <strong>TinyCraft Town</strong> is a simple 2D pixel art survival game focused on light resource management, crafting, and exploration. Gather materials, cook food, fish, build workstations, craft weapons and gear, and restore a small ruined village. Inspired by games like RuneScape, Valheim, and Conan Exiles—without the complexity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a <strong>relaxing crafting sim</strong> with satisfying progression, cozy visuals, and no pressure — just you, your tools, and a world to rebuild.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.poster.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.webm?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/cef1666645eef0c5814460dd278f52cb.mp4?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.poster.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.webm?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/56290debc8c1c71389b54df55d6047bc.mp4?t=1758393080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3314780/extras/c454ff4d6c670fad4388c5396d968bd2.avif?t=1758393080\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>🪓 What will you do?</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🛠️ <strong>Gather & Craft</strong> – Chop wood, mine ores, and create workstations and tools to fuel your progress.<br>🏘️ <strong>Rebuild the Town</strong> – Fix abandoned buildings to unlock new features, recipes, and characters.<br>🌱 <strong>Explore & Expand</strong> – Discover new lands and resources as you repair bridges, docks, and passageways.<br>📦 <strong>Strategic Resource Flow</strong> – Optimize your village's productivity and balance your economy.<br>🎵 <strong>Chill Atmosphere</strong> – A cozy pixel world with a soothing soundtrack, perfect for relaxed play sessions.<br>♻️ <strong>Early Access Evolving World</strong> – Frequent content updates and new systems on the horizon.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you enjoy games like <strong>Forager</strong>, <strong>Travellers Rest</strong>, or <strong>Stardew Valley</strong>, but want something more <strong>focused on crafting and calm progression</strong>, TinyCraft Town is the perfect escape.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧰 Whether you're here to optimize or just to unwind — your village awaits.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Thank you so much for your visit! I'm a solo indie game developer and I am doing my best to improve the game based on the community feedback. By purchasing the game you are encoraging me to keep making games even better. Best wishes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
